                            <comment id="16166147" author="jking3" created="Thu, 14 Sep 2017 12:11:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Builds still are not stable on Travis; fortunately Appveyor is doing okay.  The centos-7.3 image jobs are randomly hanging.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
